To run (the easy way):

1) Open <PATH_TO_THE_PROJECT_DIRECTORY>/offline_solution/index.html as a local file in your browser


To run (a slightly more involved way):

1) Install node: follow the instructions at http://howtonode.org/how-to-install-nodejs
2) Install npm: follow the instructions at https://github.com/isaacs/npm
3) cd into the root directory of the project
4) Run "npm install" to install dependencies
5) Start the app: node app.js
6) Open localhost:3000 in your browser (or 10.0.2.2:3000 if running a VirtualBox)